Gerar KEY
openssl rand -hex 32

Prepare system:
ansible-playbook -i inventory.yml prepare.yml

To configure:
ansible-playbook -i inventory.yml k3s-cluster.yml
ansible-playbook -i inventory.yml pihole.yml

Remover PiHole:
ansible-playbook -i inventory.yml pihole-cleanup.yml

Reiniciar:
ansible-playbook -i inventory.yml reboot.yml

Desligar:
ansible-playbook -i inventory.yml shutdown.yml

Destroy everything:
ansible-playbook -i inventory.yml cleanup-k3s.yml

Se formatar os sistemas:
Limpar a tabela DHCP Lease do pfSense e:
ssh-keygen -R 172.20.0.61; ssh-keygen -R 172.20.0.62; ssh-keygen -R 172.20.0.63; ssh-keygen -R 172.20.0.64
